## When building components
- Always check the SRS v2 document for exact specs before building any component
- Build in the order defined in SRS Section 10.2 (Phase 1 → Phase 12)
- Every section's text content is fetched from DB via API — never hardcode copy
- All hover states must use transition duration 200ms ease
- All cards: radius 16px, border 1px solid #D6D3F0, hover shadow 0 8px 32px rgba(96,85,217,0.12)
- Ghost section numbers: position absolute, top-right, Syne 800, color rgba(96,85,217,0.06), pointer-events none

## Do NOT
- Do not use NextAuth — auth is custom JWT only
- Do not use any CSS framework other than Tailwind
- Do not hardcode any text content — everything comes from DB/API
- Do not use CSS filter:invert() on any logo/image
- Do not use localStorage for JWT tokens
- Do not create files outside the defined structure above
- Do not use default Next.js blue theme anywhere
